@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
title What the guard is allowed to look at

package "Bitcoin guard" {
  [The key you hand over] as BK
  [A simple lock check] as BL
}
note bottom of BL
  The guard sees almost nothing else.
  It cannot read a note or the receipt.
end note

package "Cardano guard (Validator)" {
  [The sticky note on the chest\n(Datum)] as D
  [The note you hand over\n(Redeemer)] as R
  [The WHOLE shopping receipt\n(Context)] as C
  [Coins going in] as IN
  [Coins going out] as OUT
  [Who signed] as S
}
C --> IN
C --> OUT
C --> S
note bottom of C
  The guard reads the whole receipt,
  but not other people's chests.
end note
@enduml
